OL,3,CThe death of Pope Francis is a time of
OL,4,Csorrow, but also one of gratitude
OL,6,FIt was a moment I will never forget.
OL,8,FIt was 2014, and I'd been invited to
OL,9,Fmoderate a conference on human
OL,10,Ftrafficking at the Pontifical Academy
OL,11,Fin the Vatican gardens.
OL,13,FThe then Home Secretary Theresa May
OL,14,Fwas there - alongside key figures in
OL,15,Fthe Church, leading law enforcement
OL,16,Ffigures and crucially, survivors who'd
OL,17,Fcome to share their stories.
OL,19,FAs the conference wrapped up, the man
OL,20,Fwho'd inspired it arrived.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
