OL,3,CThe death of Pope Francis is a time of
OL,4,Csorrow, but also one of gratitude
OL,6,FHe'd pulled up in his Ford Focus
OL,7,Foutside.
OL,9,FHe spent some time chatting to the
OL,10,Fcleaners on the way in. He didn't want
OL,11,Fthe fancy Papal chair from which to
OL,12,Faddress the room.
OL,14,FITV News Presenter Julie Etchingham
OL,15,Ffirst met Pope Francis in 2014 at a
OL,16,Fconference on human trafficking
OL,18,FThere was a deep hush when he came
OL,19,Finto the conference hall, and I
OL,20,Fwondered where he was going to sit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
