OL,3,CThe death of Pope Francis is a time of
OL,4,Csorrow, but also one of gratitude
OL,6,FWhat was immediately noticeable was
OL,7,Fhow quickly he departed from his
OL,8,Fspeech notes (I could peer over his
OL,9,Fshoulder at them).
OL,11,FHe spoke with passion, directly. The
OL,12,Fissue of modern slavery and human
OL,13,Ftrafficking was right at the heart of
OL,14,Fhis papacy - and this was Pope Francis
OL,15,Fspeaking from the heart.
OL,17,FHe was issuing a challenge to everyone
OL,18,Fin the room to make a difference. It
OL,19,Fwasn't a gentle message of
OL,20,Fencouragement - this was a mission he
OL,21,Fexpected us to join.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
