OL,3,CThe death of Pope Francis is a time of
OL,4,Csorrow, but also one of gratitude
OL,6,FAt the end of this remarks the room
OL,7,Fwas on its feet in applause.
OL,9,FIt then descended into what I've
OL,10,Fbecome familiar with at the Vatican
OL,11,Fover the years - a sort of friendly
OL,12,Fchaos as the Pope made clear he was
OL,13,Fhappy to be greeted individually by
OL,14,Feveryone in the room.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
