OL,3,CThe death of Pope Francis is a time of
OL,4,Csorrow, but also one of gratitude
OL,6,FArgentinian Police Chiefs, thrilled to
OL,7,Fmeet their fellow countrymen, queued
OL,8,Fup alongside religious sisters who
OL,9,Fwere beaming and laughing. FBI chiefs
OL,10,Fgave the pope one of their caps.
OL,11,FTheresa May queued alongside the
OL,12,FCardinals and the priests.
OL,14,FEach of us was given a rosary. I have
OL,15,Fmine in my desk drawer still.
OL,17,FI will always be grateful to the press
OL,18,Fsecretary of Cardinal Vincent Nichols
OL,19,Fwho had arranged for us to be allowed
OL,20,Fto bring an ITV News camera crew with
OL,21,Fme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
