OL,3,CThe death of Pope Francis is a time of
OL,4,Csorrow, but also one of gratitude
OL,6,FIt was too good an opportunity not to
OL,7,Fsee if the pope would go on camera.
OL,9,FAs the pope got ready to leave, we
OL,10,Fmanaged to position ourselves by the
OL,11,Fdoor - Cardinal Nichols winking and
OL,12,Fwaving at me to get ready as he
OL,13,Fsteered the Pope towards us.
OL,15,FWe got our few words - he gave it both
OL,16,Fbarrels when I asked him if he had a
OL,17,Fmessage for those responsible for
OL,18,Fhuman trafficking.
