OL,3,CThe death of Pope Francis is a time of
OL,4,Csorrow, but also one of gratitude
OL,6,FI've been fortunate to meet Pope
OL,7,FFrancis several times since then. It
OL,8,Fwas always a warm and joyful encounter
OL,9,F- in later years of course he's made
OL,10,Fall his greetings from his wheelchair.
OL,12,FEvery time without fail he said "Pray
OL,13,Ffor Me" - and I've learned he said
OL,14,Fthis to nearly everyone who had an
OL,15,Fencounter with him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
