OL,3,CThe death of Pope Francis is a time of
OL,4,Csorrow, but also one of gratitude
OL,6,FFor the Church it is a hard moment to
OL,7,Fbear - of sorrow and uncertainty of
OL,8,Fwho comes next.
OL,10,FIt is a sorrow I share, but a time of
OL,11,Fgratitude too for a man who gave an
OL,12,Fexample of holy service, humanity and
OL,13,Flove to all who met him. I feel very
OL,14,Fblessed to have been one of them.
